{
  "stem": "12052.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And over there, the-- the conditions were bad, where you had-- if-- if you could sleep, then the bed bugs would-- would eat you alive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what the Germans didn't take your blood, the bed bugs would take the blood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when-- so sometime, I was lucky enough, I said I had a shift to run or repairs, and so I stayed in the machine room, where it was warm from the hot iron, you see.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The red hot iron come in big box and going through.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I slept-- I made myself a bed on a piece of board about so big between two pipes where the steam was coming through the big steam engines.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I slept, and I knew the bed bugs wouldn't be, and I could sleep warm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only, every time an ingot-- this means that ingot, big like this chair-- would go in-- in the rolling mills, every time [CHUCKLES] they shake-- shake the board with you on it, there was nice, warm, cozy, and the bed bugs would not eat you.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was pretty lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some winter times I could sneak over and sleep over, what was very unusual to-- to let you do it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Clothing was tough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just what I wear on myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't have the-- the prison uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had all kinds of-- we-- we got from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And shoes, what-- what we could, what we got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I worked a lot with oil, the-- the most steam engines.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after the shift was-- was-- oil soaked in clothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Matter of fact, sometimes you get, from the oil, like small infections and so.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
